Sentencas: Oxygen ion conducting solid electrolyte thin film of BIMEVOX family Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 was synthesized by an innovative and cost effective spray pyrolysis technique on alumina substrate.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The uniformity in deposition is obtained by propane-2ol assisted atomization.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: Thermal decomposition behavior of precursors was studied using thermogravimetric analysis (TGA and DTA).
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The room temperature stabilized pure gamma-phase Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 was obtained by annealing films at 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The phase of the material is confirmed by XRD.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The morphological studies were done using SEM.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: DC electrical conductivity measurements were done with respect to temperature to reveal the onset for ionic conduction and it was found to be about 420 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The AC conductivity measurements were also done using impedance spectroscopy in the frequency range 100 Hz to 1 MHz and in temperature range 228-550 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The ionic conductivity was found to be increasing with temperature.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: It was of the order of 21.16 S m(-1) at 550 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The single semicircular complex impedance plot shows that the ionic conduction is through grain interior hopping mechanism.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The activation energy in high-temperature region was found to be 0.36 eV which is lower than other methods of synthesis.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: Which is very much favorable for usage of these films in low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Synthesis of fuel cell grade Bi2Co0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films
